review_text: Great playground for kids my daughter loves it
Water sprinklers are great for the kids. Usually always busy with families park around. Ice cream truck usually around
It used to be a nice playground. Its always littered. Adults seem to drink beer and smoke dope and trash the place.
Love it the water park for the kids is amazing
Great that they have the sprinklers on all day!!!!!
Not overly crowded. Spray ground is great for summer.
